Testing Topics
--------------

# List all available topics
$ ls cmd/tdh/topics/

# List topics through CLI
$ ./bin/tdh help topics

# Test a specific topic
$ ./bin/tdh help <topic-name>

# Test option topics (strips option- prefix)
$ ./bin/tdh help dry-run  # Finds option-dry-run.txxt

